snippet.title: Official Checkout: Cashier Simulator Trailer (Updated)
snippet.description:
Wishlist Checkout: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2969140/Checkout_Cashier_Simulator/

Checkout is a cozy point-and-click game where you step into the shoes of a supermarket cashier. Scan, bag products, and collect payment to earn as many points as you can before your shift ends. Unwind between shifts and get to know a colorful cast of coworkers.
